data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the prestigious Fox Bank Plantation! Nestled within this picturesque community, this exquisite residence offers the perfect blend of luxury and tranquility, featuring a sprawling 67-acre lake, walking trails, and an array of amenities. Step inside and discover an inviting interior designed for both comfort and style. The heart of the home is the spacious and well-appointed eat-in kitchen nook, equipped with stainless steel appliances and a convenient gas range. Perfect for casual family meals or entertaining guests, this kitchen is a chef's delight. No detail was left unturned as a formal dining room & half bath also occupy the bottom floor, providing space for hosting family & friend gatherings.Escape to the tranquility of three bedrooms upstairs, each thoughtfully designed for rest and relaxation. The master suite features an ensuite bath with a luxurious garden tub, providing a private retreat. The additional 2 bedrooms lie just off of the connecting loft, each featuring walk in closets. An additional bathroom/bath combo & laundry room top off the second floor.   Step outside into your own private paradise. The large backyard, fenced-in, provides the ideal setting for outdoor activities, family barbecues, or simply unwinding after a long day.   Fox Bank Plantation offers an unparalleled living experience with a variety of amenities to enrich your lifestyle. Enjoy leisurely strolls along the walking trails, take in the serene views of the 67-acre lake, or partake in community events. This neighborhood also provides easy access to schools, shopping centers, and medical offices, ensuring convenience at your fingertips.  Additional features of this home include abundant natural light throughout, modern appliances, and finishes. The cozy fireplace adds warmth and charm, creating a perfect ambiance for both quiet nights and festive gatherings. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional residence your new home. Contact us today to schedule a private showing and embrace the beauty and comfort that Fox Bank Plantation has to offer!
